  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study evaluates three best-practice care pathways for postnatal depression (PND) by
      comparing sole General Practitioner (GP) management to GP management in combination with
      CBT-based counselling from either a Psychologist or a Maternal and Child Health Nurse (MCHN).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
